# 📖 Chapter 16 – Google Analytics 4 (GA4)

---

# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum Google Analytics 4 (GA4) ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki GA4 kya hota hai, website par user behavior kaise track kiya jata hai, reports kaise analyze karte hain aur business decisions lene ke liye analytics data ka practical use kaise kiya jata hai.

---

# 16.1 What is Google Analytics 4 (GA4)?

**Google Analytics 4 (GA4)** Google ka free analytics tool hai jo website aur app par users ke behavior ko track karta hai.

Simple Words:

> **GA4 = Website par users kya kar rahe hain uska complete analysis.**

GA4 batata hai:

* Kitne visitors aaye.
* Kahan se aaye.
* Kis page par gaye.
* Kitni der website par rahe.
* Kya action liya.
* Conversion hua ya nahi.

---

# 16.2 Why GA4 is Important?

SEO sirf traffic lana nahi hai.

Traffic ko understand karna bhi zaruri hai.

Benefits:

* User Behavior Analysis
* Traffic Source Tracking
* Conversion Measurement
* Audience Insights
* Marketing Performance
* Business Decisions

