# 16.5 Important Metrics

### Users

Unique visitors.

---

### Sessions

Ek user ki website visit.

---

### Engaged Sessions

Aisi sessions jahan user actively interact karta hai.

---

### Average Engagement Time

User average kitni der website par active raha.

---

### Event Count

Kitni baar events trigger hue.

---

### Conversions (Key Events)

Business goals complete hone ki count.

Examples:

* Contact Form Submit
* Phone Call Click
* WhatsApp Click
* Purchase

---

# 16.6 Traffic Acquisition

GA4 batata hai traffic kahan se aa raha hai.

Examples:

* Organic Search
* Direct
* Referral
* Social
* Paid Search
* Email

Isse pata chalta hai kaunsa channel best perform kar raha hai.

---

# 16.7 User Acquisition

Ye report batati hai ki new users kis source se aaye.

Useful for:

* SEO
* Ads
* Social Media
* Email Marketing

---

# 16.8 Engagement Report

Ye report batati hai:

* Most Visited Pages
* Average Engagement Time
* Events
* User Activity

Agar kisi page par engagement kam hai, to us page ko improve karna chahiye.

---

# 16.9 Events

GA4 event-based tracking use karta hai.

Common Events:

* Page View
* Scroll
* Click
* Form Submit
* Video Play
* File Download

Custom events bhi create kiye ja sakte hain.

---

# 16.10 Conversions (Key Events)

Important business actions ko conversion mark kiya ja sakta hai.

Examples:

* Contact Form Submission
* Quote Request
* WhatsApp Click
* Call Button Click
* Product Purchase

Conversions business performance measure karne me help karti hain.

---

# 16.11 Audience Reports

Audience Reports se users ke baare me insights milte hain.

Examples:

* Country
* City
* Device
* Browser
* Age (where available)
* Language

Ye marketing strategy improve karne me help karta hai.

---

# 16.12 Real-Time Report

Real-Time report batati hai ki is waqt website par kya activity chal rahi hai.

Useful for:

* Campaign Testing
* Tracking Verification
* Live Monitoring

